items.title: Mint Mobile - No Id Required Options
items.snippet: Mint Mobile offers prepaid plans with no ID verification required for activation. Simply purchase a SIM card with cash at any retail location.

items.title: Mint Mobile - Anonymous Options
items.snippet: Get anonymous prepaid service with Mint Mobile. No personal information needed for basic plans under $50/month.

items.title: Mint Mobile - Prepaid Options
items.snippet: Mint Mobile prepaid plans start at $15/month. Activation can be done online or in-store with minimal information.

items.title: Mint Mobile - Cash Payment Options
items.snippet: Pay with cash at thousands of Mint Mobile retail locations. No credit check or bank account required.
